1
00:00:03,850 --> 00:00:07,910
As long as I have the power to protect 
my friends, that's all I need.

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:12,490
If I could trade for that power, 
I wouldn't care how weak I was.

3
00:00:15,910 --> 00:00:18,030
I guess... that's contradictory.

4
00:00:19,350 --> 00:00:20,440
You are an interesting one.

5
00:00:21,250 --> 00:00:23,820
I wish I could fight you fair and square.

6
00:00:24,720 --> 00:00:25,500
What do you mean?

7
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:28,040
I mean that time is up.

8
00:02:02,190 --> 00:02:04,100
Previously on Fairy Tail:

9
00:02:04,650 --> 00:02:08,400
Each side presses the other as the 
battle on Tenroujima continues.

10
00:02:08,850 --> 00:02:12,030
Bluenote appeared before Natsu's group.

11
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:17,290
He's not one of the 7 Kin of Purgatory, 
but the second-in-command!

12
00:02:17,550 --> 00:02:21,240
The odds were stacked higher 
and higher against Fairy Tail.

13
00:02:21,860 --> 00:02:27,350
But then Fried, Bickslow, and 
Gildarts came running back.

14
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:30,300
Fairy Tail started to gain some momentum.

15
00:02:30,740 --> 00:02:35,600
But then something happened on Tenroujima 
that no one could have even imagined...

16
00:02:35,980 --> 00:02:39,350
The land where Fairy Tail's 
founding master rests...

17
00:02:39,350 --> 00:02:43,600
What future could Mavis's will 
illuminate for Fairy Tail?

18
00:02:56,090 --> 00:02:56,580
Damn it...

19
00:02:57,490 --> 00:02:58,910
What the hell is happening?

20
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:02,930
P-Power... I can't gather any strength...

21
00:03:03,740 --> 00:03:05,560
All the energy from my body 
is being drained suddenly...

22
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:08,910
What in the world is happening?

23
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:13,550
Cana? Cana!

24
00:03:13,900 --> 00:03:15,680
Hey, answer me!

25
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:21,000
I'm... so weak...

26
00:03:21,670 --> 00:03:23,370
I can't keep... my eyes open...

27
00:03:23,660 --> 00:03:25,900
This is strange...

28
00:03:25,900 --> 00:03:28,970
Even though I secretly ate some 
fish just a little while ago...

29
00:03:28,970 --> 00:03:33,500
I'm beat... I think I'm done...

30
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:34,140
Happy!

31
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:36,330
Could... this be...?

32
00:03:36,770 --> 00:03:38,450
Our magic power?

33
00:03:56,090 --> 00:03:58,400
What was that shaking before?

34
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,150
Azuma, I suppose.

35
00:04:03,030 --> 00:04:05,250
My strength... It's being drained.

36
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:08,070
Sounds like he felled the Tenrou Tree.

37
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:14,840
He's stealing the magic power from all 
the people with the mark of Fairy Tail.

38
00:04:15,810 --> 00:04:16,900
What?

39
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,040
What the hell is happening?

40
00:04:19,580 --> 00:04:22,620
I suspect this was an 
order from Master Hades.

41
00:04:23,250 --> 00:04:25,030
Why am I helping her?

42
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,290
I don't really know myself.

43
00:04:30,410 --> 00:04:32,580
Erza vs. Azuma!

44
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:38,730
You fiend!

45
00:04:39,190 --> 00:04:43,550
I have control over the island's magic 
power, but have left yours alone.

46
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,760
Now, Titania.

47
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:48,230
All around the island, your 
comrades are facing certain death.

48
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:53,480
You shall show me just how great this 
"power to protect your friends" is.

49
00:04:54,450 --> 00:04:57,020
You called yourself Azuma, one 
of the 7 Kings of Purgatory, yes?

50
00:04:57,810 --> 00:04:59,190
Why did you do this?

51
00:04:59,610 --> 00:05:01,320
It was Master Hades's orders.

52
00:05:02,610 --> 00:05:06,160
He told us to get rid of every Fairy 
Tail wizard, without exception.

53
00:05:07,090 --> 00:05:07,610
No!

54
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:10,950
Why is it that you purposefully 
left me free to act?

55
00:05:11,290 --> 00:05:11,950
I told you why.

56
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,530
I want to fight you seriously.

57
00:05:16,110 --> 00:05:16,950
That's all.

58
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:21,340
If that is the truth you speak,

59
00:05:21,340 --> 00:05:25,590
then the moment I defeat you, you 
will return everyone's power!

60
00:05:26,250 --> 00:05:27,270
That, I promise.

61
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:30,790
Honestly, this is not how I 
would prefer to do things.

62
00:05:33,770 --> 00:05:36,560
But that's only if you win, of course.

63
00:05:38,110 --> 00:05:40,150
My friends' lives lie in the balance!

64
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,490
I assure you, I...

65
00:05:42,740 --> 00:05:43,300
...will win!

66
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,760
Requip! Heaven's Wheel Armor!

67
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:47,860
Heaven's Wheel!

68
00:05:49,150 --> 00:05:50,190
Blumenblatt!

69
00:05:58,030 --> 00:05:59,600
Folium Sica!

70
00:06:03,420 --> 00:06:04,960
Ramus Sica!

71
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:17,780
This is not the Titania I was expecting.

72
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:20,440
I told you to come at me with all you've got!

73
00:06:33,730 --> 00:06:34,560
She's fast...

74
00:06:35,150 --> 00:06:37,260
Is that the Soaring Armor I've heard about?

75
00:06:37,860 --> 00:06:38,300
However...!

76
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:49,660
The Adamantine Armor.

77
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:53,860
Ultimate defense.

78
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:58,690
That's the one that defended against a 
direct hit from the Magic Focusing Cannon, Jupiter.

79
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,630
Excellent...

80
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:06,290
But can it defend against this?

81
00:07:31,010 --> 00:07:32,180
I know that one, too.

82
00:07:32,810 --> 00:07:33,770
The Thunder Empress Armor.

83
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:37,600
I see now. Your magic power does 
justice to your name, Titania.

84
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:42,830
Quick Requipping, and flawless swordsmanship.

85
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:50,340
I'm impressed. This is quite enjoyable.

86
00:07:52,550 --> 00:07:54,110
So this is Great Tree Ark magic...

87
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:55,490
This will be a challenge.

88
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:59,560
I see! It seems you are not just all talk.

89
00:08:00,220 --> 00:08:02,270
You aren't obessed about 
people's strength for nothing.

90
00:08:03,050 --> 00:08:04,650
Will you fight me at full strength now?

91
00:08:05,140 --> 00:08:08,590
But that won't be enough to stop me!

92
00:08:55,460 --> 00:08:56,800
Her magic power's increasing?!

93
00:09:02,710 --> 00:09:05,610
I can't break through even with the 
magic power of the Purgatory Armor?

94
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:10,680
You seem to have overestimated 
your armor's power.

95
00:09:11,290 --> 00:09:12,690
You were completely unguarded from below!

96
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:15,970
Tower Burst!

97
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:44,420
This man... What incredible magic power!

98
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:47,030
He is truly strong.

99
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:51,060
The Fairy's Armor is still damaged...

100
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:54,690
And I don't have any other armor 
that'll be a match for him.

101
00:09:55,920 --> 00:09:56,600
What'll I do?

102
00:09:58,500 --> 00:09:59,370
Now that I think about it...

103
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:03,970
I bought that Seduction Armor last week.

104
00:10:04,850 --> 00:10:05,490
With that, I might...

105
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:10,600
I refuse!

106
00:10:10,930 --> 00:10:12,390
I'm not Lucy, damn it!

107
00:10:12,860 --> 00:10:13,920
Talking to yourself?

108
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:17,380
So then, what should I do?

109
00:10:18,460 --> 00:10:23,230
To overcome his magic power, I have to 
collect all of mine and focus it into an attack.

110
00:10:25,450 --> 00:10:27,750
I can't use any magic power for defense.

111
00:10:38,540 --> 00:10:40,150
Therefore, I won't use any defense!

112
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:42,700
I will concentrate all of 
my magic into my sword!

113
00:10:46,550 --> 00:10:49,560
A sword you can't even grip unless 
you discard all defense...

114
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:53,750
Behold, the Fairy Sword, Benizakura!

115
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:02,390
My defeat means defeat for the guild!

116
00:11:03,530 --> 00:11:05,040
This will be my last stand!

117
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:07,530
Come, Titania!

118
00:11:08,050 --> 00:11:09,060
I cannot lose!

119
00:11:11,010 --> 00:11:12,050
This is for the guild!

120
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:15,980
I will put everything into this one attack!

121
00:11:23,580 --> 00:11:23,910
What?!

122
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:33,770
Release the magic power of "Tenrou" 
that sleeps in the great land!

123
00:11:36,250 --> 00:11:38,580
I can't move... Curses!

124
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,010
The cries of the great land...

125
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,300
Terra Clamare!

126
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:17,910
Titania... defeated.

127
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:40,730
Erza...

128
00:12:40,730 --> 00:12:42,730


129
00:12:50,860 --> 00:12:53,490
The Tenrou Tree has been destroyed by Azuma.

130
00:12:53,490 --> 00:12:56,890
Because of that, the divine 
protection that should be given

131
00:12:56,890 --> 00:12:59,140
to all who bear the mark of 
Fairy Tail has disappeared.

132
00:12:59,410 --> 00:13:03,460
In fact, their magic power is being drained.

133
00:13:04,270 --> 00:13:07,090
Fried and Gildarts are no exceptions.

134
00:13:07,540 --> 00:13:12,700
The fate of the guild lies now on 
the shoulders of one person, Erza!

135
00:13:18,580 --> 00:13:20,260
Can anyone move?

136
00:13:21,070 --> 00:13:26,220
It's no use. I don't know why, but 
my magic power is draining out of me!

137
00:13:27,070 --> 00:13:29,160
I'm dizzy...

138
00:13:29,390 --> 00:13:33,870
Does it have something to do with the 
tree on the center of the island falling?

139
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:39,050
What'll we do? Cana's completely 
lost consciousness.

140
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:42,590
Can we still make it to the camp somehow?

141
00:13:43,440 --> 00:13:44,890
Things aren't good over here, either.

142
00:13:45,660 --> 00:13:47,890
Gramps's breathing has gotten weaker...

143
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:50,940
Damn it... What's happening?

144
00:13:51,650 --> 00:13:54,280
Is everyone else safe?

145
00:14:06,300 --> 00:14:08,750
Did you say something, Siegrain-sama?

146
00:14:09,570 --> 00:14:12,040
Idiot! He's Jellal!

147
00:14:12,550 --> 00:14:15,680
That's the real identity of the 
former council member, Siegrain!

148
00:14:16,100 --> 00:14:17,810
Sorry, old habit.

149
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:21,710
He destroyed our Magic Council!

150
00:14:22,220 --> 00:14:25,710
He's a villain who made people 
lose all confidence in us!

151
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:32,500
Hey... You think he's casting 
a spell or something?

152
00:14:33,180 --> 00:14:35,320
He's in a cage made of magic sealing stone.

153
00:14:35,620 --> 00:14:38,230
He can't use magic of any kind.

154
00:14:39,300 --> 00:14:40,430
Want to test him?

155
00:14:40,930 --> 00:14:42,200
W-With what?

156
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:49,650
See, look!

157
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:52,350
He's Jellal, but he can't do anything!

158
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:54,790
C-Come on, Nadal... Stop.

159
00:14:58,150 --> 00:15:01,590
What have you been muttering to yourself?

160
00:15:14,350 --> 00:15:18,970
Now that I think about it, we haven't 
been giving you much food lately.

161
00:15:19,510 --> 00:15:21,290
You hungry or something?

162
00:15:22,700 --> 00:15:27,030
Fine. Try saying, "Please 
give me food, Nadal-sama"...

163
00:15:27,310 --> 00:15:30,130
Ask nicely, and I'll allow you to eat.

164
00:15:30,510 --> 00:15:31,000
Hey!

165
00:15:31,590 --> 00:15:35,280
And if you don't, then no meals for a week!

166
00:15:41,150 --> 00:15:42,570
Er...za...

167
00:15:46,370 --> 00:15:47,940
Don't lose...

168
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:55,370
Don't lose... Erza...

169
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:30,050
I-Impossible!

170
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:33,920
You were hit with a massive amount 
of Tenroujima's magic power!

171
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:47,440
Did I just hear Jellal's voice?

172
00:16:49,100 --> 00:16:50,350
That can't be...

173
00:16:52,340 --> 00:16:55,460
Don't be weak... He's no longer here.

174
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:58,270
Don't be misled by emotions...

175
00:16:59,150 --> 00:17:00,390
Center your mind!

176
00:17:03,450 --> 00:17:06,830
I will stand up, to protect everyone!

177
00:17:35,390 --> 00:17:36,300
Frightening...

178
00:17:49,940 --> 00:17:51,420
Do I lack the footwork?

179
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:56,060
I don't know whether I'll be able 
to win with the magic power I have.

180
00:17:57,560 --> 00:18:02,170
But the difference in "weight" 
he and I carry is great.

181
00:18:02,950 --> 00:18:06,990
Just as he says, right now, 
everyone's lives are riding on me.

182
00:18:08,590 --> 00:18:09,910
I must protect them...

183
00:18:11,070 --> 00:18:12,960
The guild... My friends!

184
00:18:13,890 --> 00:18:16,860
For their sake, I <i>will</i> win!

185
00:18:37,830 --> 00:18:39,680
You're so formidable that my heart is racing!

186
00:18:42,810 --> 00:18:45,660
Fairy Tail's Titania, Erza Scarlet!

187
00:18:46,510 --> 00:18:49,950
I am sure not to forget your 
name, as long as I live.

188
00:18:50,890 --> 00:18:51,670
Curses!

189
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:55,740
Let's name you "Erza Scarlet"!

190
00:18:56,590 --> 00:19:00,420
Scarlet. The color of your hair.

191
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,750
That way, I'll never forget.

192
00:19:03,840 --> 00:19:04,900
Move!

193
00:19:05,370 --> 00:19:07,120
It was the color of your hair.

194
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:20,010
Move!!

195
00:19:20,610 --> 00:19:22,010
This is the end!

196
00:19:23,050 --> 00:19:25,790
Have another taste of the 
magic power of Tenroujima!

197
00:19:30,570 --> 00:19:32,590
Terra Clamare!

198
00:20:12,350 --> 00:20:12,940
Erza?

199
00:20:17,350 --> 00:20:20,010
Is this... the end?

200
00:20:27,700 --> 00:20:28,900
Giving up?

201
00:20:33,120 --> 00:20:33,710
Jellal...

202
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:35,660
Erza.

203
00:20:44,800 --> 00:20:45,460
Everyone?

204
00:20:53,780 --> 00:20:54,600
I see...

205
00:20:56,100 --> 00:20:57,320
So, that's how it is...

206
00:21:02,540 --> 00:21:03,480
I apologize.

207
00:21:04,700 --> 00:21:08,710
I'd forgotten one crucial thing...

208
00:21:11,700 --> 00:21:14,100
I am not protecting everyone!

209
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:16,470
T-This is...

210
00:21:19,340 --> 00:21:25,410
It is I... who is always... being protected!

211
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:39,020
Tenroujima's magic power that I should 
have under control is protecting Erza?

212
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:42,700
Trust... Bonds...

213
00:21:45,090 --> 00:21:47,360
Her true strength...

214
00:21:49,300 --> 00:21:50,650
It is not "One", but "Many"!

215
00:21:54,350 --> 00:21:55,580
What an amazing guild!

216
00:21:57,780 --> 00:21:58,500
Excellent.

217
00:23:56,450 --> 00:23:58,350
Natsu, have you seen Gray?

218
00:23:58,350 --> 00:23:59,450
Nope, I haven't.

219
00:23:59,450 --> 00:24:02,440
Now that I think about it, haven't 
seen Juvia either. What're they doing?

220
00:24:02,440 --> 00:24:04,530
Gray and Juvia? Don't tell me...

221
00:24:04,530 --> 00:24:06,110
Haven't heard this in a while:

222
00:24:06,110 --> 00:24:08,840
They llllllike each other!

223
00:24:11,450 --> 00:24:13,470
Hey, calm down a bit, it's not <i>that</i> exciting.

224
00:24:14,220 --> 00:24:16,210
Next time: Frozen Spirit.

225
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:20,050
And besides, wasn't Juvia with Erza?

226
00:24:20,050 --> 00:24:21,770
Well, that's boring.

227
00:24:21,770 --> 00:24:23,440
What do you want to happen to Gray, exactly?

